race.comment: WANNA KISS (3) went down by a narrow margin at the latest effort and rider Larson sticks in the saddle. Strikes a winnable contest here and has to be included from the inside marble. BASSETT'S CHOICE (4) has been plying her trade in harder NSW contests and will appreciate the drop back in company here. Respect from the Waller barn. BLIGHTYS HOPE (6) finished midfield last start at Sunshine Coast. Is up in trip today and is among the chances. LADY TANGALOOMA (5) ran an improved race finishing midfield last start at Doomben when jumping at long odds. Tackles a longer journey, Thompson goes on and look for an improved run.
